comments.content:
It must be **[Dom Casual (Bold)](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018063710/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=URW&ffam=DomCasualD%20-%20Bold&fid=d524fbd6b266f26a85bc631201b5eebf&fsize=60&text=WXCR%2092.3&fit=1)** by Peter Dombrezian (1951), artificially expanded and emboldened. The URW edition looks closer to your sample
